### Create Paste - Different Languages

# JavaScript Example
POST {{baseUrl}}/paste/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "api_paste_code": "console.log('Hello, World!');",
  "api_paste_name": "JavaScript Example",
  "api_paste_format": "javascript"
}

###

# Go Example
POST {{baseUrl}}/paste/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "api_paste_code": "package main\n\nimport \"fmt\"\n\nfunc main() {\n    fmt.Println(\"Hello, World!\")\n}",
  "api_paste_name": "Go Example",
  "api_paste_format": "go"
}

###

# Rust Example
POST {{baseUrl}}/paste/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "api_paste_code": "fn main() {\n    println!(\"Hello, World!\");\n}",
  "api_paste_name": "Rust Example",
  "api_paste_format": "rust"
}

